      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Organizations</a> * Atlas Computer Laboratory</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"http://www.chilton-computing.org.uk/acl/home.htm\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/09/Atlasclsml.jpg/300px-Atlasclsml.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"110\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/09/Atlasclsml.jpg/450px-Atlasclsml.jpg 1.5x, /images/0/09/Atlasclsml.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Atlasclsml.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Atlas Computer Laboratory at Chilton <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p><b>Atlas Computer Laboratory</b>, <br />\nat <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chilton,_Oxfordshire\">Chilton site, Oxfordshire</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_Kingdom\">United Kingdom</a> was one of the major computer laboratories in the world, which operated between 1961 and 1975 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. The Chilton site campus was shared between Atlas Laboratory and the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harwell_Laboratory\">Harwell Atomic Energy Research Establishment</a>. In 1975 the Atlas Computer Laboratory was closed, moving some parts to the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daresbury_Laboratory\">Daresbury Laboratory</a> and in 1979 with the Appleton Laboratory to form the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rutherford_Appleton_Laboratory\">Rutherford Appleton Laboratory</a>. Since 2007 the Rutherford Appleton Laboratory has been operated by the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Science_and_Technology_Facilities_Council\">Science and Technology Facilities Council</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#People\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">People</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Chess_Programs\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Programs</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Conferences\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Conferences</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"People\">People</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Atlas_Computer_Laboratory&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: People\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Alex_Bell\" title=\"Alex Bell\">Alex Bell</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/John_Birmingham\" title=\"John Birmingham\">John Birmingham</a> (Harwell)</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jim_Doran\" title=\"Jim Doran\">Jim Doran</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jack_Good\" title=\"Jack Good\">Jack Good</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Peter_Kent\" title=\"Peter Kent\">Peter Kent</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/John_Waldron\" title=\"John Waldron\">John Waldron</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Programs\">Chess Programs</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Atlas_Computer_Laboratory&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Programs\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Atlas\" title=\"Atlas\">Atlas</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Master\" title=\"Master\">Master</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Conferences\">Conferences</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Atlas_Computer_Laboratory&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Conferences\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Chess_1\" title=\"Advances in Computer Chess 1\">Advances in Computer Chess 1</a> (forerunner 1973)</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Atlas_Computer_Laboratory&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Atlas_Computer_Laboratory\">Atlas Computer Laboratory from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chilton-computing.org.uk/\">Computing at Chilton: 1961-2003</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chilton-computing.org.uk/acd/home.htm\">Atlas Computing Division and Engineering: 1975-1984</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Atlas_Computer_%28Manchester%29\">Atlas Computer from Wikipedia</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Atlas_Computer_Laboratory&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chilton-computing.org.uk/acl/home.htm\">Atlas Computer Laboratory, Chilton: 1961-1975</a> </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Atlas_Computer_Laboratory\">Atlas Computer Laboratory from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228225327\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.012 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.013 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 51/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 106/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:1901-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228225327 and revision id 2540\n -->\n"
